sharkzapper-Helper is based on Grooveshark Desktop Helper for Linux ( http://github.com/intarstudents/GSDesktop-Helper )

=== Dependencies ===
aptitude install python-keybinder python-gtk2 python-gconf python

=== Usage (Ubuntu) ===
$ cd ~
$ git clone http://github.com/adammw/sharkzapper-Helper.git

Now Alt + F2 and in Run Application dialoge write:
sharkzapper-Helper/helper.py

That's it!